      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TROPICAL ETHICS (8) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Mia's Impact (20.02) in a Maiden. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Winning claims. KUNG FU ETHICS (1) is yet to break through in six starts but has run a number of placings. Finished fifth (25.99) at Maitland latest but tends to run well here despite having never won. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Should be in this for a long way. FANCY PAY CHEQUE (5) settled well back early on debut and always towards the tail to finish seventh (23.50) at Maitland over 400m. Meets a moderate line up and should do much better. FANTASY ETHICS (2) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
